tree of knowledge of good and evil.data-term: tree of knowledge of good and evil

examples.en: The house was masked by trees.
The bank was held up by masked robbers.
Masked gunmen opened fire on the bus.
Her inner turmoil was masked by an outer calm.
The masked men ghosted across the moonlit yard.
Masked raiders carried out a bank robbery today.
Three men were held hostage for two days by masked gunmen.
The new accommodation block has all but masked the original building.
Her easy disposition and sociability masked the intensity of her feelings.
Among the court entertainers waiting to enter the grand hall were masked harlequins in brightly colored pantaloons.
